    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Relative hemolysis index predictions agree with experimental data within 5% across all operating points. RH < 1 acceptance criterion satisfied at worst-case conditions. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
